18:27.920 --> 18:29.718
And then he'd be... He'd run on like...

18:30.080 --> 18:32.675
We've done his palette,
we did it in August.

18:32.840 --> 18:34.718
At some point, you might think
about doing the whole job,

18:34.800 --> 18:36.632
because that's why he's doing
what he's doing.

18:37.840 --> 18:39.035
SPORTS COMMENTATOR:
<i>Do you know what, Luke?</i>

18:39.120 --> 18:41.510
<i>I think he's been picking
