and you jump off with him,

18:54.920 --> 18:56.673
- that's fine. At least he ends.
- Yeah.

18:56.760 --> 18:59.150
SPORTS COMMENTATOR: <i>You know,
he sees in somebody like JP,</i>

18:59.240 --> 19:00.754
<i>somebody who's unbelievably loyal.</i>

19:01.200 --> 19:03.635
Don't give him a gift.
Don't give him a fucking gift.

19:04.360 --> 19:07.671
SPORTS COMMENTATOR: <i>He's become really,
