You shouldn't have to.

19:37.920 --> 19:38.990
(BELL RINGING)

19:43.120 --> 19:44.713
SPORTS COMMENTATOR:
<i>And here is AP McCoy,</i>

19:45.360 --> 19:48.159
<i>in the green and yellow hoops
of JP McManus,</i>

19:49.080 --> 19:51.037
<i>trained by JonJo O'Neil, white cap.</i>

19:53.720 --> 19:57.430
CHANELLE: <i>You see your husband
putting themselves at risk every day,</i>

19:57.960 --> 20:00.111
<i>and yes you've chosen to marry them,</i>

20:00.200 --> 20:02.317
<i>and you've chosen
to support them in the career.</i>

20:02.640 --> 20:03.869
Come on!

20:03.960 --> 20:09.274
<i>But he has lived with the hardship
