20:09.360 --> 20:12.239
<i>for the last 20 odd years he's riding.</i>

20:17.400 --> 20:18.400
- Oh!
- Oh, my God!

20:18.680 --> 20:22.230
CHANELLE: <i>His ability to control pain,
to manage pain is, um...</i>

20:23.480 --> 20:28.509
(STUTTERING) <i>Is very unique, you know,
and very bizarre.</i>

20:31.120 --> 20:35.592
<i>I mean, it is quite unusual
the way he can control concussion,</i>

20:37.360 --> 20:39.955
<i>'cause if you're out and you step down.</i>

20:40.040 --> 20:43.317
<i>And he's gone out and
ridden in the next race</i>

