20:53.440 --> 20:55.352
<i>The fear of not being champion jockey.</i>

20:55.880 --> 20:56.916
Go, go, go, go!

21:03.280 --> 21:06.478
<i>Just everything, "It's in the head,
Chanelle. It's in the head, you know."</i>

21:08.040 --> 21:11.670
<i>He's like, "Pain is temporary,
