30:48.480 --> 30:51.234
And then I was worried because
this side of my chest is fucked...

30:51.680 --> 30:54.559
(CLAMOURING)

31:00.160 --> 31:04.712
CHANELLE: <i>He's in denial but I think he's
cracked his sternum and four ribs.</i>

