Yeah.

31:08.680 --> 31:10.273
Thinking it was the most
painful thing ever.

31:11.920 --> 31:13.195
He's popped them.

31:13.840 --> 31:15.797
Come on, Evie. Get stuck in, Evie.

31:17.240 --> 31:18.310
Go on, Evie.

31:24.000 --> 31:26.959
CHANELLE: <i>Hopefully, for me,
it will be the last year but</i>

31:27.920 --> 31:31.072
<i>it's a difficult subject to, you know,
approach with him.</i>

