31:54.560 --> 31:57.837
<i>I can't force him and I wouldn't, you know.</i>

31:57.920 --> 31:59.240
<i>The decision has got to be his,</i>

31:59.320 --> 32:02.074
<i>because he's got to live
with the consequences, you know.</i>

32:18.080 --> 32:19.833
(CHATTERING)

32:24.320 --> 32:25.674
(SCREAMING)

