<i>Shut The Front Door is second.
Saint Are is third...</i>

01:23:16.520 --> 01:23:19.319
MCCOY: <i>I don't think in 20 years
I've ever been really content,</i>

01:23:20.520 --> 01:23:22.989
<i>I didn't feel I was ever as good
as I wanted to be.</i>

01:23:23.760 --> 01:23:24.989
ROBERTS: Two to jump,
he's got a chance.

01:23:25.080 --> 01:23:26.753
He's got a chance. He's got a chance.

01:23:27.600 --> 01:23:29.671
MCCOY: <i>I wish I hadn't been like that.</i>

01:23:30.400 --> 01:23:31.720
He's definitely got a chance now.

01:23:31.800 --> 01:23:33.712
He's... He's definitely got a chance now.

01:23:36.440 --> 01:23:37.999
MCCOY: <i>It would be great not to
have a care in the world</i>

01:23:38.080 --> 01:23:41.357
<i>or not have to worry about
if you're winning or not winning.</i>

01:23:42.120 --> 01:23:43.236
<i>It's not the end of the world.</i>

01:23:47.400 --> 01:23:49.517
MCCOY: <i>Winning in a lot of ways
is not the end of the world.</i>

01:23:52.200 --> 01:23:53.520
<i>But it's the end of the world for me.</i>

01:23:57.040 --> 01:23:58.679
COMMENTATOR: <i>They make
the long run in now</i>

