01:24:16.000 --> 01:24:19.755
MCCOY: <i>Now I'm starting to get it
into my thick skull that it's happened.</i>

01:24:25.080 --> 01:24:26.400
<i>The end.</i>

01:24:26.480 --> 01:24:28.119
(CHEERING)

01:24:28.200 --> 01:24:29.634
MCCOY: <i>It happens to everyone apparently.</i>

01:24:32.720 --> 01:24:34.040
<i>The end.</i>

