01:25:08.040 --> 01:25:10.555
MAN ON RADIO: <i>The last fence
in sight, tomorrow,</i>

01:25:10.640 --> 01:25:13.030
<i>the 4:25 at Sandown,</i>

01:25:13.120 --> 01:25:16.192
<i>so, for the last time
