01:25:16.280 --> 01:25:17.794
<i>Evening, AP McCoy.</i>

01:25:17.880 --> 01:25:19.075
MCCOY: Good evening, how are you?

01:25:19.160 --> 01:25:21.038
WOMAN ON RADIO: <i>Are you all right?</i>
MCCOY: I'm okay. Thanks.

01:25:21.120 --> 01:25:23.191
WOMAN ON RADIO: <i>Good. AP, we've got
a little surprise for you,</i>

01:25:23.280 --> 01:25:24.555
<i>- I hope you don't mind.</i>
